  section#section_step
    .container
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          h4  藍染製程
      .row
        .col-md-4.col-sm-12
          .step_box(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-100px);opacity: 0" data-center="transform: translateY(0px);opacity: 1")
            img(src="https://photos-2.dropbox.com/t/2/AACINzxw_bUdWit1cyZr1hepFn8zL8DX9o6TwHUC4cw-uw/12/651984139/jpeg/32x32/1/_/1/2/step01.jpg/ENq8_6YFGBUgAigC/c9Rju1Dt9kgF-FSNd6PivdOIa8p25zENp2HON2ZAgrg?size=2048x1536&size_mode=3", alt="")
            h6 step01. 採藍
            p(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-10px);opacity: 0" data-center="transform: translateY(0px);opacity: 1")  採集大菁葉，以水清洗後浸泡。夏天浸泡一天半，冬天約需四天。
        .col-md-4.col-sm-12
          .step_box(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-100px);opacity: 0" data-center="transform: translateY(0px);opacity: 1")
            img(src="https://photos-4.dropbox.com/t/2/AACF4HdKSR-ePHzDIskT08fsvgjjhN61YaQUtFyZX9YNzA/12/651984139/jpeg/32x32/1/_/1/2/step02.jpg/ENq8_6YFGBYgAigC/oJvNh3k5KO49FAYAMKhWBBv0rQTthNqP6it0GpSL9EE?size=2048x1536&size_mode=3", alt="")
            h6 step02. 打藍
            p(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-10px);opacity: 0" data-center="transform: translateY(0px);opacity: 1") 將藍葉撈除，石灰倒入浸泡液中，手動或電動攪拌至無泡沫後靜置。
        .col-md-4.col-sm-12
          .step_box(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-100px);opacity: 0" data-center="transform: translateY(0px);opacity: 1")
            img(src="https://photos-6.dropbox.com/t/2/AAD-oMIv2MXAhBLYy79VvjdH-9l6yTb453uEUAFfnT53Gw/12/651984139/jpeg/32x32/1/_/1/2/step03.jpg/ENq8_6YFGBcgAigC/M4vS7if6FNt1l_eUwgYafczZgYd0Z7B2OisnUm9QSCo?size=2048x1536&size_mode=3", alt="")
            h6 step03. 建藍
            p(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-10px);opacity: 0" data-center="transform: translateY(0px);opacity: 1") 待藍液靜置後分層，傾倒上層澄清液，下層藍泥裝入棉袋瀝乾。
      .row   
        .col-md-4.col-sm-12
          .step_box(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-100px);opacity: 0" data-center="transform: translateY(0px);opacity: 1")
            img(src="https://photos-5.dropbox.com/t/2/AADGEOR2pGFVEo9-OUrl2xTND44H_gnVrxv1sd-OpNxPyw/12/651984139/jpeg/32x32/1/_/1/2/step05.jpg/ENq8_6YFGBkgAigC/pyoLZ_RjyqfiajlzFmeEwRw4xQm8eyO58gvm81g8Qhg?size=2048x1536&size_mode=3", alt="")
            h6 step04. 建藍
            p(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-10px);opacity: 0" data-center="transform: translateY(0px);opacity: 1") 草木灰煮粳製作鹼水，倒入染缸，加入藍泥、米酒、麥芽糖等營養劑靜置發酵。每日早晚攪拌七日後綠色液面浮出藍色泡沫。
        .col-md-4.col-sm-12
          .step_box(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-100px);opacity: 0" data-center="transform: translateY(0px);opacity: 1")
            img(src="https://photos-5.dropbox.com/t/2/AAC9DX9mScifCuUplxoHf9BoX9x5HreaDBEX0jDNHDO8Vw/12/651984139/jpeg/32x32/1/_/1/2/step04.jpg/ENq8_6YFGBggAigC/F1M0l6faJtRwkVv8goNHWlHTnwLInAJ7Jt3cITJ_2Xs?size=2048x1536&size_mode=3", alt="")
            h6 step05. 染藍
            p(data-bottom-top="transform: translateY(-10px);opacity: 0" data-center="transform: translateY(0px);opacity: 1") 將精煉後的棉麻布料放入染缸重複浸泡 ( 每次兩分鐘 ) ，以及晾掛三到五次。最後以清水漂洗，浸泡醋液，晾乾燙平，完成染布。
            
